{"tid":2162793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百佳：不少入口產品來貨價升　盡量承擔上漲成本","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T20:44:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":378,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"8f79f42cb098db0fc647c62f65d2ed9c2e0d746d","tid":2162793,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"百佳超級市場回覆查詢時表示，因應疫情、市場情況及其他國家內部需求，不少入口產品來貨價及運費大幅上升，百佳盡量承擔上漲成本，維持穩定合理的產品零售價。<br />\n<br />\n百佳表示，將繼續以合理價格為顧客提供足夠的所需用品，並盡力照顧弱勢社群的需求，又指一直致力為社區不同階層提供優惠、折扣及社區支援，包括為長者提供購物優惠、推行「關愛長者食物券」，並在疫情期間，為政府及不同非政府機構提供日常用品及物資的送遞服務等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544427-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544427-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=2f111855\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544427-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=290a9d66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544427-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a134aa303804db6da5fd00901dce026336e359e7","tid":2162793,"uid":16067,"like":425,"dislike":1,"score":424,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"即係唔加就當減左"},{"pid":"9f8fc7b52d418b3a03db61f39e65b5c8993b441f","tid":2162793,"uid":9193,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"1fa08d723520171043b2423903e2c7cd1992728e","tid":2162793,"uid":61745,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:33:07.000Z","msg":"而家D野一個月加一次價咁滯"},{"pid":"f6f0d3adda15366707baa85b3450809126f6b10a","tid":2162793,"uid":262663,"like":203,"dislike":0,"score":203,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"政府覺得呢啲企業冇影響咪唔好派錢/派小啲比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets